    "body": "I'm also seeing this issue on macOS with this `starship.toml`\n\n```\n\"$schema\" = \"https://starship.rs/config-schema.json\"\n\nformat = \"$directory$character\"\nright_format = \"$command_duration\"\npalette = \"rose-pine\"\nadd_newline = false\n\n[palettes.rose-pine]\noverlay = '#26233a'\nlove = '#eb6f92'\ngold = '#f6c177'\nrose = '#ebbcba'\npine = '#31748f'\nfoam = '#9ccfd8'\niris = '#c4a7e7'\n\n[cmd_duration]\nmin_time = 1\n\n[directory]\nread_only = \" 󰌾\"\n```",
